               <provenance>The name of the original donor was erased and
                     replaced with those of Walda Kiros and Walatta Yoḥannǝs (e.g., 69ra, 73vb, 75ra, 77ra, 105va), which in turn have
                     been erased and replaced with those of Walda Māryām and Walatta Madḫǝn, in
                     brown ink. Sometimes other names, such as Gabra ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer (24ra, 33ra), are added into the supplication formulas
                     (see also Additiones 1 and 2).</provenance></history>
